          "A. Monomial",
          "B. Binomial",
          "C. Trinomial",
          "D. Quadratic"
        ],
        "answer": "B. Binomial",
        "explanation": "The expression has exactly two terms ($2y^5$ and $-y$), making it a binomial.",
        "marks": 1,
        "learningOutcomeIds": [
          "LO3"
        ],
        "topicCoverage": [
          "Classification by Terms"
